  stimulus_text = 'The speaker is addressing a group of people that she knows well.  This is evident in the way she uses the word "you" and other elements of the passage.  The speaker is also confident and self-assured.  What is the most likely reason why the writer uses a lot of short sentences in this passage? Researchers note that the pattern described above remained consistent across repeated observations, suggesting the finding was not a one-time anomaly. They caution that local conditions can still vary, yet the overall relationship held in each documented case.',
